``tool`` command:

::

    uv tool install {{ distribution_name }}

or, run directly with `uvx
<https://github.com/astral-sh/uv/blob/main/README.md>`_:

::

{%- if package_name != distribution_name %}

    uvx --from {{ distribution_name }} {{ package_name }}
{%- else %}

    uvx {{ distribution_name }}
{%- endif %}

Or, install via `pipx <https://pipx.pypa.io/stable/installation/>`_:

::

    pipx install {{ distribution_name }}

